king Manual (DMBM)</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"124\"><p>W012 -&nbsp;Remissions and remission cancellation quality assurance</p></td><td width=\"146\"><p>Recovery /&nbsp;Work list manager</p></td><td width=\"99\"><p>As advised by senior management</p></td><td width=\"98\"><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam71086\">SAM71086</a></p></td><td><p>See the Debt Management and Banking Manual (DMBM)</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"124\"><p>W013 -&nbsp;Potential transfer cases</p></td><td width=\"146\"><p>Processing/Recovery or Technical /&nbsp;Clerical processing officer / Clerical caseworker</p></td><td width=\"99\"><p>Weekly</p></td><td width=\"98\"><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam71088\">SAM71088</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam103070\">SAM103070</a></p></td><td><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam103071\">SAM103071</a></p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"124\"><p>W014 -&nbsp;Bankruptcy or voluntary arrangement cases</p></td><td width=\"146\"><p>Recovery /&nbsp;Clerical caseworker</p></td><td width=\"99\"><p>Monthly</p></td><td width=\"98\"><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam71090\">SAM71090</a></p></td><td><p>See the Debt Management and Banking Manual (DMBM)</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"124\"><p>W015 -&nbsp;Open appeals</p></td><td width=\"146\"><p>Processing/Technical /&nbsp;Appeals handler</p></td><td width=\"99\"><p>Monthly</p></td><td width=\"98\"><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam71092\">SAM71092</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam10170\">SAM10170</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam11150\">SAM11150</a></p></td><td><p>-</p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"124\"><p>W016 -&nbsp;Manu