SAM113010</a></p></td><td><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam113011\">SAM113011</a></p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"124\"><p>W032 -&nbsp;RLS cases</p></td><td width=\"142\"><p>Recovery /&nbsp;Clerical caseworker</p></td><td width=\"99\"><p>Daily /&nbsp;weekly</p></td><td width=\"99\"><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam71114\">SAM71114</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam101340\">SAM101340</a></p></td><td><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam101031\">SAM101031</a></p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"124\"><p>W033 -&nbsp;Transfer to COP security review.&nbsp;<strong>Note:</strong> Currently not used</p></td><td width=\"142\"><p>Processing /&nbsp;Clerical processing manager</p></td><td width=\"99\"><p>Daily</p></td><td width=\"99\"><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam71116\">SAM71116</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam141040\">SAM141040</a></p></td><td><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam141041\">SAM141041</a></p></td></tr><tr><td width=\"124\"><p>W034 -&nbsp;Sundry charge quality check.&nbsp;<strong>Note:</strong> Currently not used</p></td><td width=\"142\"><p>Processing /&nbsp;Clerical processing manager</p></td><td width=\"99\"><p>Monthly</p></td><td width=\"99\"><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam71118\">SAM71118</a>&nbsp;and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam140050\">SAM140050</a></p></td><td><p><a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/hmrc-internal-manuals/self-assessment-manual/sam140051\">SAM140051</a></p></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><a href=\"#Top\">Top of page</a></p>\n<h2><a id=\"IDALXXLH\" class=\"spTaxHMRCAnchor\">W035 - W044</a></h2>\n<table summary